{"tid":2220693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"限聚令599G? 駛乜驚呀","createTime":"2020-09-28T00:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T00:59:24.000Z","uid":70964,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5efe7499ef1f389bb2f2d25089e14dd0d4f243","tid":2220693,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/umLAacW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FumLAacW.jpg&h=542ac77e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mjvo3xX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjvo3xX.jpg&h=d1767965&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，昨日好耐無同兩老飲茶 ，又近中秋，所以帶他們去飲茶 食下月餅<br />\n<br />\n入到去酒樓<br />\n全場爆滿  又話只限全場50%入座率 ? 不用了<br />\n<br />\n一家八口樂也融融<br />\n分枱坐?不用了<br />\n最搞笑塊膠牌放喺個轉盤上當分隔咗<br />\n但塊牌識轉架喎  笑死人<br />\n<br />\n本來想報狗處理，但最後都打消呢個念頭<br />\n班狗黎度實隻眼開隻眼閉 反而調番轉頭拉我尋釁滋事， 捉我送中，不了"},{"pid":"91218a6b742358590e53a5f901eb44251e8d93cc","tid":2220693,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:12:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f691bdfdda9f0d7f374e9615ed7a6fdd8dd7e40","tid":2220693,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd9cbdd907c4fb540d4573644452a7b715cdae41","tid":2220693,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa772dc3bd8794f3939b5e226d436e14fc661864","tid":2220693,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec60eb2d9930e444e73b252cdbb44cb024d9d4cb","tid":2220693,"uid":151525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:31:25.000Z","msg":"幫襯藍店?"},{"pid":"67bb7ccdedcc99f557f5a60eb0fb4a3b60923673","tid":2220693,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"推你老味咩"},{"pid":"328e2aafbf3890a0c481abee7e81fbe2